flowchart LR
    DEPLOY[Deploy trigger]

    DEPLOY --> BUILD[build + test]
    BUILD -->|fail| HALT[halt + notify]
    BUILD -->|pass| STAGE[deploy to staging]
    STAGE --> SMOKE[smoke tests]
    SMOKE -->|fail| ROLLBACK[rollback to previous]
    SMOKE -->|pass| CANARY[canary slice 5%]
    CANARY --> MONITOR[monitor SLOs 10 min]
    MONITOR -->|degraded| ROLLBACK
    MONITOR -->|healthy| PROMOTE[promote 100%]
    ROLLBACK --> ALERT[alert on-call]
